
=== README for BuildGear ===


1. Introduction

   BuildGear is a lightweight embedded build system for experienced GNU/Linux
   hackers and developers. The primary focus of this build system is to keep it
   simple, which is reflected in a straightforward command line build interface,
   and easy to maintain build files. The secondary focus is build performance
   and build integrity. BuildGear is easy to use and well suited for product or
   prototype development.


2. Installation

   See INSTALL file for details on how to build and install BuildGear.


